Cabify Logo Cabify is a Spanish ridesharing company which provides vehicles for hire via its smartphone mobile app. Vehicles are driven by self-employed service providers. Operating in Spain, Portugal and Latin America, the company offers two services, one for businesses and another for individuals. Cabify was founded in May 2011 by Juan de Antonio, and raised a total of $304 million from investment funds. Source
